00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
We'd rather have you two up in arms.

113
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
What are you looking at?

114
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Go back.

115
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Don't expect me

116
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
To let you in or something.

117
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You're forgetting something. You're my Aunt. You love me so much.

118
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I've forgotten everything, m'boy!

119
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I've been ordered

120
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Not to care about who you are to me.

121
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
That's who you are today - no one!

122
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I don't even know you!

123
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I tell you, if I got furious --
-Aye? What are you gonna do?

124
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I --

125
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I won't set foot in here!

126
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Don't.

127
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
No one over here

128
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gives two hoots.

129
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Get going!

130
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Back to your Dado!

131
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Double time!

132
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Okay, bye.

133
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Bye.

134
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I swear, Maheen...

135
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He brought flowers for you.

136
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
And some perfume.

137
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He said he wanted to make peace.

138
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He said he was ready to hear everything you'd say quietly.

139
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Where's the flowers? And the perfume?

140
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Mum destroyed the flowers

