00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
What's up with Nano? Doesn't she want the kids making peace?

148
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Wait.

149
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Lemme have a look.

150
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Hmm!

151
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Mhm...

152
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Hello?

