205
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
How'd I know?

206
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I do, Suraiyya Begum.

207
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
His mind may be English,

208
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
