00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Who'd he name?

211
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You sitting or standing?

212
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Standing, Ammi Begum.

213
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Take a seat.

214
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Okay?

