226
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gotta say, though.

227
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I've got her to hear it!

228
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
What you could never say!

229
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
It's okay.

